Attribute.Name: Operario
Attribute.Expression: (select u.operario from sgauser u where u.iduser = sgacdoc.modifiedby)

Attribute.Name: Estadolineas
Attribute.Expression: (select decode (sgacdoc.estado, 'D', decode ((select sum(numlineas) from sgavcdocldoclbultoenproceso v where v.iddoc = sgacdoc.iddoc), 0, sgacdoc.estado, 'P'), sgacdoc.estado) estadoLineas from dual)
